Package halo.userinterface.cmdline

Provides for the handling of user input and starting of corresponding calculations.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
CmdFilterData Serves as interface between Data manipulation tools and command line input
CmdHalfLife Serves as interface between command line input and calculation of half-lives
CmdNormalization Serves as interface between command line input and tools for calculation of linear regression
CommandLine Class which forwards information from command line input to further classes which serve as interface between command line and tools for calculation
